quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  37,145,Nuko tumujugunya ku butaka bw’agasi ameze nk’umurwayi
  37,146,Maze aho yari ari tuhameza uruyuzi rwera ibihaza (kugira ngo rumugirire akamaro)
  37,147,Nuko tumwohereza ku bantu ibihumbi ijana cyangwa banarenga
  37,148,"Maze baremera, nuko tubaha umunezero w’igihe gito"
  37,149,"Ngaho (yewe Muhamadi) babaze uti “Ese Nyagasani wawe afite abakobwa gusa, hanyuma bo bakagira abahungu"
  37,150,Cyangwa twaremye abamalayika b’abakobwa babireba (ikaba ari yo mpamvu bavuga ko abamalayika ari igitsina gore)
  37,151,Mu by’ukuri no mu binyoma byabo (ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) baravuga (bati)
  37,152,“Allah yarabyaye (bavugaga ko abamalayika ari abakobwa ba Allah)” Nyamara rwose ni abanyabinyoma
  37,153,None se (ni ukubera iki) yaba yaratonesheje abakobwa akabarutisha abahungu
  37,154,Ese mwabaye mute? Amahitamo yanyu ashingira kuki
  37,155,Ese ntimutekereza
  37,156,Cyangwa mufite ibimenyetso bigaragara
  37,157,"Ngaho nimuzane igitabo cyanyu, niba muri abanyakuri"
  37,158,"Kandi banashyize isano hagati Ye (Allah) n’amajini, nyamara amajini yo azi neza ko azazanwa (imbere ya Allah kugira ngo acirwe urubanza)"
  37,159,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,160,Uretse abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera (ni bo batajya bagira ibyo bamwitirira)
  37,161,"Bityo, mu by’ukuri mwe (ababangikanyamana) ndetse n’ibyo mugaragira bitari Allah"
  37,162,Nta n’umwe (mu bemeramana) mushobora kuyobya
  37,163,Uretse abazajya mu muriro ugurumana
  37,164,Kandi nta n’umwe muri twe (abamalayika) udafite umwanya uzwi (mu ijuru)
  37,165,Mu by’ukuri twe (abamalayika) dutonda imirongo (dusali nk’uko Abayisilamu babigenza)
  37,166,Kandi mu by’ukuri ni twe dusingiza (Allah)
  37,167,Kandi mu by’ukuri (ababangikanyamana b’i Maka) bajyaga bavuga bati
  37,168,“Iyo tuza kugira urwibutso tuvanye ku bo hambere (mbere y’uko intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa)
  37,169,Mu by’ukuri twari kuba abagaragu ba Allah b’imbonera.”
  37,170,Nyamara (nyuma y’uko Qur’an ibagezeho) barayihakanye kandi vuba aha bazaba bamenya (ukuri)
  37,171,"Kandi rwose, isezerano ryacu ku bagaragu bacu b’Intumwa, ryaje mbere"
  37,172,Ko mu by’ukuri ari bo bazatabarwa
  37,173,Ndetse ko mu by’ukuri ingabo zacu ari zo zizatsinda
  37,174,"Bityo rero (yewe Muhamadi), birengagize igihe runaka"
  37,175,"Maze ubahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,176,Ese ibihano byacu ni byo bashaka kwihutisha
  37,177,"Nyamara ubwo bizabamanukiraho, kizaba ari igitondo kibi ku baburiwe"
  37,178,"Bityo rero (yewe Muhamadi), birengagize igihe runaka"
  37,179,"Unabahozeho ijisho, kuko bidatinze bazabona (ibihano)"
  37,180,"Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyagasani Nyiricyubahiro! Nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamwitirira"
  37,181,Kandi amahoro nabe ku Ntumwa (zose za Allah)
  37,182,"Kandi ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  38,1,Swad! Ndahiye iyi Qur’an yuje urwibutso
  38,2,Nyamara abahakanye bari mu bwibone n’ubwigomeke
  38,3,"Ese ni ibisekuru bingahe tworetse mbere yabo, bigatakamba by’impitagihe"
  38,4,(Abarabu b’ababangikanyamana) batangajwe no kugerwaho n’umuburizi (Muhamadi) ubakomokamo. Nuko abahakanyi baravuga bati “Uyu ni umurozi w’umubeshyi.”
  38,5,"“(Arafata) imana (zacu) zose akazigira Imana imwe? Mu by’ukuri, iki ni ikintu gitangaje!”"
  38,6,Maze ibikomerezwa muri bo bigenda bivuga biti “Nimugende mutsimbarare ku mana zanyu. Mu by’ukuri iki ni ikintu gikenewe.”
  38,7,Ibi ntitwigeze tubyumva mu myizerere yo hambere. Ibi nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari ibihimbano
  38,8,"Ese ni we wenyine muri twe waba waramanuriwe urwibutso? Ahubwo barashidikanya ku rwibutso rwanjye (Qur’an), kuko batarumva ku bihano byanjye"
  38,9,"Ese baba bafite ibigega by’impuhwe za Nyagasani wawe, Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Ugaba bihebuje"
  38,10,"Cyangwa baba bafite ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’ibiri hagati yabyo? Niba ari uko bimeze, ngaho nibazamuke mu kirere bakoresheje uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose (maze bakumire ubutumwa)"
  38,11,Zimwe mu ngabo z’udutsiko zizakubitirwa inshuro aha ngaha (nk’uko iz’udutsiko ari ko byazigendekeye mbere)
  38,12,"Mbere yabo, abantu ba Nuhu, aba Adi ndetse na Farawo wari ufite inyubako zisongoye (piramide) barahinyuye"
  38,13,"N’aba Thamudu, abantu ba Lutwi ndetse n’aba Ayikat (b’i Madiyani), bose bari udutsiko"
  38,14,"Nta na kamwe muri two katahinyuye intumwa, nuko ibihano byanjye biba impamo"
  38,15,Aba nta kindi bategereje kitari urusaku rumwe rudasubira
  38,16,Kandi baravuze bati “Nyagasani wacu! Twihutishirize umugabane wacu (ibihano) mbere y’uko umunsi w’ibarura ugera.”
  38,17,"Ihanganire ibyo bavuga (yewe Muhamadi), kandi wibuke umugaragu wacu Dawudi wari umunyembaraga (mu guhangana n’umwanzi). Mu by’ukuri yicuzaga kuri Allah cyane"
  38,18,Mu by’ukuri twashoboje imisozi gufatanya na we (Dawudi) kudusingiza buri uko bwije n’uko bucyeye
  38,19,"Ndetse n’inyoni zikusanyirijwe hamwe, zaramwumviye (zifatanya na we mu kudusingiza)"
  38,20,"Maze dukomeza ubwami bwe, tunamuha ubushishozi no guca imanza neza"